		<title>Quantum Motion Raises $160 Million for Quantum Growth</title>
		<link>https://ventureburn.com/quantum-motion-raises-160-million-for-quantum-growth/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Ekemini]]></dc:creator>
